    "This limitation arises from the static nature of the examples in DIN, which involve vocabularies from other databases rather than Mondial.",
    "C3+DIN was the highest among all experiments, totaling $58.19.",
    "C3+Din with GPT-4 exhibited the same overall accuracy as DIN, albeit lower than C3 with GPT-4.",
    "Whereas the strategy proved effective for simple queries, it inherited the issues of both C3 and DIN, such as prolonged table and column recall times and large prompt sizes.",
